Results.PublicRemarks: First time to market in 35 years! This home has been lovingly lived in and cared for by same family for past 35 years. Home was stripped to the studs in 2016, exterior re sheeted with 1/2 inch plywood, plus insulated with 1/2 inch foam insulation and new siding installed. Roof re shingled with fibreglass shingles in 2017.New 200amp electrical panel in 2018. Dual head mini split  heat pumps installed in 2021. One in eating area and the other in rec room. Spacious eat in kitchen has beautiful solid maple cabinets and newer appliances. Main living area oak hardwood floors in like new condition. The living room has non functioning wood burning fireplace (vendors will not be providing wett certification, it is as is) would be great for a propane insert though. There is a convenient half bathroom off the kitchen. Upstairs there are 3 bedrooms including spacious master with his and her closets, and full family bathroom. There is also a lot of closet space upstairs as well. The basement is fully developed with large rec room and mini split. (There is a wood stove used by vendors, but it is as is) There is a large storage room and spacious laundry room. There is also storage closets off the rec room. Outside drive in rear access to utility shed and larger 12 x 20 shed. This is a very functional family home and move in ready for sure! (25182250)

The main floor has 2 bedrooms, open concept living & dining room, which opens to a patio, designed for you to enjoy optimal views of the ocean. The full-siized basement offers you a large recreation room, third bedroom & is roughed in for a 2nd bathroom. The exterior shed is ideal for storing your recreational vehicles or shed parties with friends. Dare to dream of sitting on your patio or living room watching the sensational sunsets! Close to the city and amenities.  Ideal location! More than a home: a lifestyle! (25183421)
